result.title: Training 1
result.content:
Salam!

Avalin training e CF etoono inja gozashtim. Ye seri soale ke bayad halleshoon konin. Baziash ro baziatoon sare class zadin :D. Soala aksaran graph an. Say konin roo hamashoon vaght bezarin ta DFS BFS etoon ghavi she. Soali, moshkeli, chizi dashtin ham haminja begin.

Hamin dige, Khosh begzare ;)
